		<description>
Tool for automatic satellite assembly embedding (as resources). Satellite assemblies will automatically be loaded from resource section and no longer need to be manually deployed with the executable.
If you use Fody.Costura this may interest you as well (or vica versa).
Any project this is added to will have it's satellite assemblies embedded as resources into the dll/exe itself.
During runtime the injected code will auto. resolve them so everything works the same as always, except you don't have to deploy all those "language code" folders anymore.

Requires .Net 4 or above.
		</description>
